Language Transcriber / 语言转写

This project does not copy or redistribute VocoType proprietary code.

The local speech models used by this project are expected to come from the
public FunASR / ModelScope model repositories. If you copy already-downloaded
models from your local machine, keep the original model names and source notice.

Known local model names:
- iic/speech_paraformer-large_asr_nat-zh-cn-16k-common-vocab8404-onnx
- iic/speech_fsmn_vad_zh-cn-16k-common-onnx
- iic/punc_ct-transformer_zh-cn-common-vocab272727-onnx

FunASR source:
https://github.com/modelscope/FunASR

FunASR model license:
https://raw.githubusercontent.com/modelscope/FunASR/main/MODEL_LICENSE

DeepSeek is accessed through an OpenAI-compatible HTTP API. Users must provide
their own API key and comply with DeepSeek's terms.
